"><FONT SIZE=2><EM><FONT COLOR="#000000"><FONT FACE="Times New Roman, serif"><FONT SIZE=3>Geberth V.</FONT></FONT></FONT></EM><FONT COLOR="#000000"><FONT FACE="Times New Roman, serif"><FONT SIZE=3> Psychological profilling. - Law and Order, 1981. - P. 29, 46-49. </FONT></FONT></FONT></FONT></FONT> </P> <P CLASS="western rust13" ALIGN=JUSTIFY > <FONT FACE="Courier New, monospace"><FONT SIZE=2><EM><FONT COLOR="#000000"><FONT FACE="Times New Roman, serif"><FONT SIZE=3>Geberth V.</FONT></FONT></FONT></EM><FONT COLOR="#000000"><FONT FACE="Times New Roman, serif"><FONT SIZE=3> Practical homicide investigation. Tactics, procedures, and forensic techniques. (3-rd ed.), Elesevier. - N. Y., 1996. </FONT></FONT></FONT></FONT></FONT> </P> <P CLASS="western rust13" ALIGN=JUSTIFY > <FONT FACE="Courier New, monospace"><FONT SIZE=2><EM><FONT COLOR="#000000"><FONT FACE="Times New Roman, serif"><FONT SIZE=3>Keeney </FONT></FONT></FONT></EM><EM><FONT COLOR="#000000"><FONT FACE="Times New Roman, serif"><FONT SIZE=3>В</FONT></FONT></FONT></EM><EM><FONT COLOR="#000000"><FONT FACE="Times New Roman, serif"><FONT SIZE=3>., Heide K.</FONT></FONT></FONT></EM><FONT COLOR="#000000"><FONT FACE="Times New Roman, serif"><FONT SIZE=3> Gender differences in serial murderers. A preliminary analysis. - Journal of Interpersonal Violence, 1994, Vol. 9, №3. - P. 383-398. </FONT></FONT></FONT></FONT></FONT> </P> <P CLASS="western rust13" ALIGN=JUSTIFY > <FONT FACE="Courier New, monospace"><FONT SIZE=2><EM><FONT COLOR="#000000"><FONT FACE="Times New Roman, serif"><FONT SIZE=3>Lane </FONT></FONT></FONT></EM><EM><FONT COLOR="#000000"><FONT FACE="Times New Roman, serif"><FONT SIZE=3>В</FONT></FONT></FONT></EM><EM><FONT COLOR="#000000"><FONT FACE="Times New Roman, serif"><FONT SIZE=3>., Gregg W.</FONT></FONT></FONT></EM><FONT COLOR="#000000"><FONT FACE="Times New Roman, serif"><FONT SIZE=3> The new encyclopedia of serial killers. Headline Book Publishing. - London, 1996. </FONT></FONT></FONT></FONT></FONT> </P